title: Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Pink Dial Ladies Watch FE1140-86X - Overview
description:
Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Pink Dial Ladies Watch - FE1140-86X http://www.abt.com/product/92568/Citizen-FE114086X.html

Classic lines and a hint of sophistication allow for this Citizen Silhouette Crystal timepieces to stand out. Shining bright with Swarovski crystals and featured in a stainless steel case and bracelet with blush pink dial. Includes date feature.
Specifications:
• Movement: Eco-Drive J710
• Functions: 3-Hand with Date
• Band: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel Bracelet Fold Over Clasp with Push Button
• Case Size: 29mm
• Case Material: Silver-Tone Stainless Steel Swarovski Crystal Bezel
• Dial: Metal Dial
• Crystal: Spherical Crystal
• Water-Resistance: 0050M
